Senior Credit Analyst Manager - PT SMFL Leasing Indonesia
Senior Credit Analyst Manager  -
Senior Credit Analyst Manager
Responsibilities
Contribute to the preparation/review of credit policy and strategy documentsExpected to progress by demonstrating a skill of high standard in the credit analysis and the presentation of such analysis independentlyReview credit request package/programs submitted for Credit Committee approval under delegated credit authorityAnalyze credit requests and review proposed facilities structure and making the credit reportOversee development and implementation of risk-management plans, in line with local regulatory requirementsEnsure that credit request packages/programs are in line with set strategy, policies and guidelinesOversee independent assessment and monitoring of risk, in compliance with applicable laws, rules and standards within the GroupEnsure the integrity and quality of data and data analysisManage the overall credit portfolio to ensure it is in line with the risk appetiteEnsure daily monitoring reports are generated, disseminated, followed-up and filed appropriately  Requirements :Age between 35 –45 years oldAt least 5 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this positionPreferably Manager Assistant/Manager specializing in Leasing company or equivalentHave experience in leasing company and credit area (Finance companyStrong leadership and ability to manage subordinatesStrong communication and presentation skillStrong analytical skills and strategic personFluent in English is a must, both oral and written  A comprehensive remuneration package, allowances and bonus are offered to the candidates who meet qualification. Only short-listed candidates are welcome to apply.Please send your application along with your Curriculum Vitae, Photograph, and copy Certificates to:PT. SMFL LEASING INDONESIAHuman Resources DepartmentSummitmas II, 12th Fl, Jln. Jend. Sudirman Kav.61-62Jakarta Selatan 12190Or email to:isaac.nyoman@smfl.co.id
